I can't open my store.

29:21.515 --> 29:24.394
Nobody else is gonna do this, either.
It's not just me.

29:24.551 --> 29:27.054
Listen, I'll give you the coat. I'm sorry.

29:29.456 --> 29:31.265
- Okay?
