29:36.597 --> 29:38.634
Here. Happy birthday.

29:39.466 --> 29:42.914
- Ooh. What, no china?
- Come on, open it.

29:45.505 --> 29:47.382
It's an accounting program!

29:47.975 --> 29:50.731
Well, your gifts just keep
getting better and better and better.

29:50.811 --> 29:52.484
Thank you. I'm glad you like them.

29:52.679 --> 29:53.988
And I have one for you.

29:54.381 --> 29:56.088
- You didn't.
- I did.

29:56.750 --> 29:57.751
Senna!

29:59.887 --> 30:02.766
