32:14.955 --> 32:16.628
$50,000 preapproved.

32:17.424 --> 32:18.425
How...

32:19.826 --> 32:23.283
It's really not a big deal. And now
you'll have access to enough money

32:23.363 --> 32:25.352
so you and your mom don't kill each other.

32:25.432 --> 32:27.674
- Hey. Your mom's the killer.
- Alleged killer.

32:29.202 --> 32:31.079
If you need a minute to look it over...

32:32.672 --> 32:34.242
No, it...

32:36.243 --> 32:38.519
- Yeah, it looks good.
- Okay.

32:39.079 --> 32:43.450
