right here, and we're good.

32:57.097 --> 32:59.737
- Perfect.
- Thank you for bailing me out.

33:00.233 --> 33:02.270
Well, I wasn't going to, but Darla begged.

33:08.341 --> 33:12.790
Oh... Darla and Steve are taking me
