36:50.730 --> 36:55.488
It is called living in the moment,
and maybe you, sir, should give it a try.

36:55.568 --> 36:56.842
I am plenty in the moment.

36:57.937 --> 37:00.179
You are the opposite of in the moment.

37:17.957 --> 37:18.958
Not always.

37:29.769 --> 37:32.716
<i>There's certainly no shortage
of things to want.</i>

37:33.173 --> 37:35.915
Better house, better car, better boobs.

37:38.478 --> 37:40.973
I suppose,

37:41.854 --> 37:44.240
